    "body": "This happens if Metamask has a different chainId configured for the localhost network. You have to change Hardhat's chain id to match the one used by Metamask:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nnetworks: {\r\n  hardhat: {\r\n    chainId: 1337\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nYou might still see some failed `eth_call`s in the node. I don't know why that happens; seems like a Metamask issue.",
